                    - patient-1_adqu-type_adqu-date_O(S/D).tiff
                - OCTA
                    ...
                - retinography
                    - patient-1_retinography_adqu-date_O(S/D).jpg
                - patient-1_analysis.json
            - study_23-1-2022
                ...
        - patient-2
            ...
        - ...
    - MS
        ...
    - NMO
        ...
    - RIS
        ...
```


